  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13051978/austria_mayrhofen_sporthotel-strass_spa.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5ee950274ab94eff9ae97aa186bb5853" /></p>
<p>Ski and then sit back and sauna - What better way to live the life of luxury than to unwind after a day on the slopes by relaxing by a thermal pool, sipping champagne and taking time out in the sauna. </p>
<p>You can enjoy fine dining by the fire or soak up the mountain side scenery whilst enjoying a cocktail in a Jazz Bar. </p>
<p>Whatever your choice be, we offer some fantastic, luxurious ski and spa getaways that will make you feel like you're living the high-life without any effort required on your part.</p>
<p>With outstanding 4* and 5* Hotels across some of Europe's most stunning ski and snowboard destinations, you can enjoy a luxury ski holiday with Inghams. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski holiday deals</a></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><img style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;" src="/media/13065653/drinks.jpg" alt="herobanner" data-udi="umb://media/5656eae1437d4f6f90768234bbd945d0" /></h3>
<h3>What makes an Inghams luxury ski holiday: </h3>
<p>There are many aspects that can make you feel like you are on the most luxurious holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>5* hotels</strong> - For a truly elevated holiday, select a hotel or chalet that offers everything from rooftop hot-tubs, private saunas or champagne on arrival.</li>
<li><strong>Michelin Dining</strong> - Some of our resorts are renowned for being the location of Michelin star restaurants.</li>
<li><strong>Ski-in ski-out</strong> - many of our hotels, chalets and apartments offer a ski-in ski-out experience, meaning no walks to the nearest ski lift.</li>
<li><strong>Childcare</strong> - some of our accommodation offers on-site childcare if required.</li>
<li><strong>Room upgrade</strong> - feel extra special and ask our reservations team what room upgrades are on offer at your accommodation.</li>
<li><strong>Private shuttles</strong> - a selection of our top accommodations include a private shuttle bus to take you to the nearest ski lifts, resort centre or the local ski school. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Some of the best Luxury Hotels</h2>
<p>A collection of the accommodation options from some of our resorts, put together for you to help you find the right accommodation for your perfect luxury and spa holiday:</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: left;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73}" title="Romantik Hotel">Romantik Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13074240/jacuzzi.jpg" alt="romaus" data-udi="umb://media/516f059a6ff7407498a76572ef8db652" /></p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">An adult only 'Emotion Spa' area with saunas, steam room, infrared cabin and spacious, romantic relaxation room.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Full of charm and attractive traditional features, it has a warm and welcoming - close to the town centre and lake.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Interconnecting indoor/outdoor pool, as well as beauty treatment rooms.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Cosy bar with open fire to relax and unwind after a day of skiing or snowboarding on the mountains.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: left;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b7198b31bf694a12ad16bb2d29451234" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7198b31bf694a12ad16bb2d29451234}" title="Hotel Les Grandes Rousses">Hotel Grandes Rousses</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13073749/_v7a1857.jpg" alt="grafra" data-udi="umb://media/0943b73d77e7433e891ce72feabd0e0d" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A panoramic restaurant with an excellent reputation and you can even dine in the unique out-door heated pods.</li>
<li>Outdoor terraces with wonderful views, including an outdoor heated swimming pool, cosmic sauna and whirlpool.</li>
<li>The exclusive Spa des Alpes with a sensory pool and six treatment rooms.</li>
<li>A Cocktail bar with live evening music and a lounge with an an open fireplace. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn">France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e999c381739e4b27ad6e9b9aa65a0b3b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e999c381739e4b27ad6e9b9aa65a0b3b}" title="Hotel Aaritz">Hotel Aaritz</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13084444/103287.jpg" alt="aarita" data-udi="umb://media/504f22debd894a5cab5433ba79d084a1" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>A grand staircase leads down to the lounge with a log-burning fireplace and comfy sofas, the perfect place to enjoy a warming hot chocolate</span><a data-udi="umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449}" title="Delta Whistler Village Suites"></a></li>
<li><span>Bedrooms come with balcony views over the valley or the village, with bathrobes and slippers</span></li>
<li><span>A wellness area with a pool, sauna and Turkish bath. Beauty treatment rooms for massages</span></li>
<li><span>An unbeatable location right in the centre of Selva and directly opposite the Ciampinoi gondola</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy" class="c-btn">Italy</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e74cf27714834da9b35d5d8afce6670b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e74cf27714834da9b35d5d8afce6670b}" title="Walliserhof Grand Hotel &amp; Spa"><span>Walliserhof Grand Hotel &amp; Spa</span></a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13079780/walliserhof-grand-hotel-spa-artists-impression-lobby-reception.jpg" alt="walswi" data-udi="umb://media/fd937cb0bbcb4e2197f6cca4eda4abcf" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A superb 2,100m² spa complete with swimming pool, various saunas, a steam bath, a whirlpool and a light-flooded relaxation area.</li>
<li>Walliserhof has recently undergone extensive renovations and is now ready to show you its new design and unique concept.</li>
<li>Attractive bar and lounge with open fireplace.</li>
<li>Pianist can be found playing some evenings as a relaxing, musical backdrop to your cocktail hour.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn"><span>Switzerland</span></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288}" title="Hotel Piolets">Hotel Piolets Park</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103282/hotel-piolet-527x283.jpg" alt="HotelPiolet" data-udi="umb://media/7f44745b75f745bf93ce1fd3e7d5ea87" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>With a spa that was refurbished in 2019 to high standards and quality finish.</span></li>
<li><span>A regular shuttle bus directly from the hotel to take you to the ski lifts.</span></li>
<li><span>A classic lounge bar with a roaring fireplace, perfect for evening cocktails or afternoon après out on the terrace.</span></li>
<li><span>The hotel has a passion for gastronomy with an extensive choice and display cooking using quality ingredients.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra" class="c-btn"><span>Andorra</span></a> <a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9"> </a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc}" title="Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie"><span>Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie</span></a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13075749/savoie-bed-_0.jpg" alt="savoiehotel" data-udi="umb://media/f3aa6ba98f284b86b8f8cd66b725d881" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>An indoor swimming pool and loungers were you can relax with mountain views.</span></li>
<li><span>A wellness area with whirlpools, a sauna and a steam room.</span></li>
<li><span>A short walk to the Solaise Express lift for the Solaise / Le Fornet side of the ski area, or the Olympique gondola if you want to ski across towards Tignes.</span></li>
<li><span>5 course evening meals, including pre-dinner apèritif, choice of complimentary wines with dinner followed by tea/coffee.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn"><span>France</span></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
