<p style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Whilst many look to go away skiing purely for the slopes-based action itself, there are others that look to either combine it with spa and relaxation or concentrate solely on relaxation.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The great thing about spa and relaxation is that every resort and every country are always looking to offer top-notch facilities including: steam rooms, saunas, pools, hot tubs, whirlpools and even gyms. On top of this many hotels offer treatments, meaning that after a hard day's skiing you can come back to enjoy a nice pre-dinner massage.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Nearly all our Hotels have spa facilities and treatments, but many of our chalets are also equipped with a sauna or hot tub as we look to give our guests the best facilities to relax. We are aware how important it is to feel refreshed in order to get the most out of a holiday, therefore we always recommend looking into the spa and relaxation options that your chosen accommodation has to offer.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Additional selections:</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cffe266796604c0bafe480490de7b519" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cffe266796604c0bafe480490de7b519}" title="Adler Spa Resort Dolomiti"><strong>Adler Spa Resort</strong></a> - <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/4321e3c95c3546dbaf4ad18e85b63ca6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4321e3c95c3546dbaf4ad18e85b63ca6}" title="Hotel Fanes">Hotel Fanes</a></strong> - <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/67ba36a931fc4fac83b977d22cb30b13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67ba36a931fc4fac83b977d22cb30b13}" title="Hotel Seehof">Hotel Seehof</a></strong> - <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/a56ad61f053d46b5a56ca8cc1faef5ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a56ad61f053d46b5a56ca8cc1faef5ec}" title="Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa">Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa</a> </strong>- <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bb6c0b3c6cc04ea3aa186ac9e66d3674" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb6c0b3c6cc04ea3aa186ac9e66d3674}" title="CGH White Pearl Lodge &amp; Spa"><strong>White Pearl</strong></a> - <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Luxury &amp; Spa skiing FAQs </h2>
<p><strong>What is the service like?</strong> - Expect high-end, 5* star service on our luxury skiing and snowboarding holidays, with warm welcomes, professional staff and stunning locations. </p>
<p><strong>What is the catering like?</strong> - Enjoy an abundance of quality food whilst on holiday, either at your accommodation or opt to visit Michelin star restaurants in resort if you want an extra special experience. </p>
<p><strong>What makes the accommodation special?</strong> - From private chalets to 5* star hotels - you can expect rooms with spectacular views to cosy lounges with open fires and inspiring designed bedrooms.</p>
<p><strong>What facilities are there?</strong> - All of our Luxury accommodation choices offer a range of spa facilities (ski and spa as we like to say). You find swimming pools, saunas, hot tubs and more at our selection of apartments, chalets or hotels.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
